      "name": "Do you service the Macedon Ranges?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes — we service the full Macedon Ranges including Woodend, Kyneton, Romsey, Gisborne, Riddells Creek, Lancefield, Mount Macedon, Macedon, Spring Hill, Carlsruhe, Malmsbury, Taradale, Tylden and surrounds. Call 0476 302 729 to confirm your address."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How much does a chimney clean cost in the Macedon Ranges?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
