        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes — a significant share of our work in the Ranges is holiday homes, weekenders and short-stay rental properties. We're used to coordinating access with owners who live elsewhere and working around rental calendars. The irregular use pattern common in holiday homes actually increases creosote risk — long idle periods followed by heavy use are harder on a flue than consistent regular use."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is there a call-out fee for the Macedon Ranges?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
